    <text id="B1236T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>Brower asks for transportation home for an elderly Staunton resident after his
                    surgery in Richmond.</p>
            </div1>
        </front>

        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                <head>
                    <name type="recipient"><abbr expan="Brevet Lieutenant Colonel">Bvt. Lt.
                        Col.</abbr> J. J. DeLamater,<lb/><unclear>
                            <abbr expan="Surgeon United States Army">Surg. U.S.A.</abbr>
                        </unclear>
                        <abbr expan="Surgeon in Chief">Surg. in Chf.</abbr>
                        <abbr expan="Bureau of Refugees, Freedmen and Abandoned Lands">B.R.F.
                            &amp;c</abbr><lb/>District of Virginia</name>
                </head>

                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <date value="1867-06-24">June 24th 1867</date>
                        <name type="place">Howard's Grove Hospital<lb/>Richmond, <abbr expan="Virginia"
                            >Va.</abbr></name>
                    </dateline>
                    <salute>Colonel</salute>
                </opener>

                <p>I have the honor to request Transportation to <orig reg="Staunton"
                    >Stanton</orig>, <abbr expan="Virginia">Va.</abbr> for Henry Williams <add
                        hand="h1" place="inline">aged</add> indigent Freedman now at this Hospital.</p>

                <p>He came to this Hospital for the purpose of being operated on for Cataract, which
                    operation has been done successfully and he is now ready to return to his home.</p>

                <p>If Transportation is furnished him the Government will be relieved of the Expense
                    of his Support.</p>

                <closer>
                    <salute>Very respectfully<lb/><abbr expan="Your Obedient Servant">Yr. Obdt.
                            Servt.</abbr></salute>
                    <signed>D.R. Brower<lb/>A.A. <abbr expan="Surgeon">Surg.</abbr>
                        <abbr expan="United States Army">U.S.A.</abbr><lb/><hi rend="underline">Chg.
                            Hospital</hi></signed>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
    </text>
